{"tid":1712411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教育界罷課","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T14:32:08.000Z","uid":268988,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8699f6d7411f872553d08a0d04ef08cfc5ac8598","tid":1712411,"uid":268988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"❗❗❗❗等吾切 13/11 教育界罷課🆘🆘🆘🆘❗❗❗<br />\n<br />\n你哋好，我哋係一群被良知喚醒既老師，懇請大家用一分鐘時間消化尼個訊息，有關今日中午所發出的Google Form(以下連結) 感激大家各校同工的參與同表態，現在有268人表示參與13/11 罷工，總共有65間學校表決，這數字証明，你們不是孤單！你願意叫你身邊既同事，一齊放下手上既功作，去為前線學生踏出尼一步嗎？你們願意為我們擋子彈，我們願意為你罷工，香港人冇得輸！教育界醒覺未？ 暴政殘殺孩子⋯⋯我地仲沉默就=幫兇<br />\n<br />\n已經去到危急關頭，請和富既老師，我哋眼見香港現在發生既事，已經吾係去到五個月前眼見既為政治抗爭，現在引致既係去到校園內，罔顧莫視學生既安全，我哋再吾企出黎行尼步，對吾對得住學校入面既學生。懇求大家，為我哋下一代既著想，我哋必須聯合一齊，聽日一齊Black Bloc 罷工。<br />\n<br />\n我哋學校支持既人吾單止係尼11位同事 我哋既然都決定罷，一定會令更多吾敢發聲既人企出黎!<br />\n<br />\n暫時更新至22:00 的罷工統計<br />\n<br />\n✅Please fill in the following form for data collection.<br />\nWe will release all info to all of you here so that you will know how many of your colleagues are willing to strike together.<br />\n把握實際人數，先可以迫到學校停課<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdI19KHhtolmmDoB5GpnYSEzO3MzfTy3aq3Ca0EPnPZFnUe4Q/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdI19KHhtolmmDoB5GpnYSEzO3MzfTy3aq3Ca0EPnPZFnUe4Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7ZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=b98ad9a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdI19KHhtolmmDoB5GpnYSEzO3MzfTy3aq3Ca0EPnPZFnUe4Q/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n❗❗ 可能大家有既concern係會比人清算，所以留意翻填google form 吾洗一定用google account address去填同可以匿名。最後其實係想要實際罷既罷工數字。如果大家見同一間學校既老師都肯行動，大家信心會多好多<br />\n顯示較少"},{"pid":"ee7fa4599f23f8ed01a6a6b2c78197f0ffb01429","tid":1712411,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"我想講一講既係防暴分區唔係用18區<br />\n而係港島、東九、西九、新界南、新界北<br />\n<br />\n暴大所在既沙田, 屬於新界南<br />\n如果想用區暴動去救佢的話<br />\n可以吹雞 荃+葵+青+東涌+沙+馬+火炭呢啲集中暴動<br />\n拉對角線最長距離去打<br />\n<br />\n其他區保持有零散開花去迫佢留住兵力<br />\n<br />\n而家集中晒沙田大埔<br />\n沙田屬新界南<br />\n大埔屬新界北<br />\n只會被兩區輕取....<br />\n就算十八區開花要開得有智慧<br />\n//<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC%2F&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7ZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=93b867e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC/</a>"},{"pid":"1316533286aa24972191d0b840d20c3439e70241","tid":1712411,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"遠水不能救近火！！只係各地開花，班狗可以用無警時份唔理你！！<br />\n<br />\n分頭行事！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力反包！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擋水炮車！！</span><br />\n另小隊開花！嘗試分散警力！做得幾多得幾多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中大地理難去，但去到就去！人多就咩都有可能！求下大家！！"},{"pid":"9801947d6c562782a5aa9b8e83d34809f100b1b3","tid":1712411,"uid":32505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"救人<br />\n罷課"},{"pid":"b24d050f97fa79c2e3c515676b6ac0ef4aa61160","tid":1712411,"uid":63206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da204d0a8d630caabd60e3d6b7dfd8784f9aacc2","tid":1712411,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"171833a8304b0ac1eda1ae70d66d3efb147c6b0c","tid":1712411,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e9b997afcbbfd27e43618d0e53700bf345d937d3","tid":1712411,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3cb34d3e3246f9cd8a4d365a634e27c1015f984","tid":1712411,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"34d8d53bf561ee0ea89c45ac10d27025e9eba827","tid":1712411,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT